CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1958, pg. 3 reads: "2. Westinghouse High co-eds, Elnedia Monroe, Marianna Stroud, Betty Love and Lillian Thompkins sample Meadow Gold buttermilk poured by Sherlynn Dudley"
TitMainTitle: Sherlynn Dudley serving Meadow Gold buttermilk to Elnedia Monroe, Marianna Stroud, Betty Love, and Lillian Thompkins, in Syria Mosque for the 1958 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
